description: CAA Proceedings, that are peer-reviewed and published within one year of the conference. Conference proceedings have been published since 1973. Greetings from Perth, CAA 2013! We are happy to announce that CAA proceedings are now available online. At the moment, the collection of proceedings is not complete yet; we expect this to be finished somewhere in the course of 2013.
